# Exception: tracked snapshot of ASAP-approved brand list. Captures
# point-in-time approval state with git history (when was each brand
# added — see commits referencing tmp/asap_approved_brands.json).
# Regenerable via scripts/diagnostics/asap-list-brands.js or probe-asap.js,
# but the live ASAP API doesn't preserve approval-date history, so the
# snapshot stays tracked. Other tmp/ contents remain ignored as before.
!tmp/asap_approved_brands.json

